global                               command                              global

NAME
     gglloobbaall - declare global variables

SYNOPSIS

     gglloobbaall nnaammee [[ nnaammee ...... ]]

DESCRIPTION

     Declares nnaammee to be a global symbol.  A global symbol retains its value
     outside of statement blocks.  If nnaammee is used as an array name, each
     element of the array is global.

EXAMPLE

     gglloobbaall CCOOUUNNTT__RRAATTEE

